data.description: Remodeled Top to Bottom! 4 bedroom, 3 bath Main House, 1 bedroom, 1 bath Guest House. All New Exterior Stucco, Block Fence, Gates, New Dual-Pane Windows, New Doors. All New Paint, Tumbled Travertine Flooring, New Cabinets, Granite Counter Tops. All New Bathrooms with New Tubs, Toilets and Tile Shower Surrounds and Faucets. New Lighting and Ceiling Fans. Brand New Roof. New Stainless Steel Gas Range.
